game.name: Mini Brain Doctor
game.description: Get ready to operate on Mini brain and learn how to use the coolest medical tools ever! Start preparing Mini for surgery by taking his temperature, pulse and getting rid of his hair. Now everything is set! Cut into Mini head and use cool machines to find and exterminate germs and other fun things. See if you can make Mini feel better and have fun being the best surgeon!
